Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:21.83,ep,NTP,0,0,0,,追 忆 之 笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 拉紧钢索
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 那边太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不要随便放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动 到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.77,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边 放那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 货物都在那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 移动到那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以都叫你别用飞的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要切断钢索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你能自己想点办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何处理你的居住权 我们尚无定论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你能暂时在这里生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 在这种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种地方太不方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 就 行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在 Chamber 附近 方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是账单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,账 单？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求贵官通过劳动补偿对机库造成的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 莉吉特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我们赶走海贼的可是雷德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏机库和那是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 雷德刚刚来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不了解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们为他免除了逗留期间所消耗的水电费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及将这庞然大物放在船上的装载费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是只有单方受益的霸王交易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我具体内容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这台人形机器人太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移动 到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 去搬下一箱货物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放到刚刚那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber 移动到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说不要飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这人形机器人不赖嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙听得懂你之外的人说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的话他也会听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据军纪 在允许范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可移交命令权
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板 我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的快递哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 在干活在干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.62,0:05:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙搞啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让破废铁干活 自己却在一边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个大蠢材 果然还是应该把他丢进海里…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家可能只是在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法从贵官的行动中发现意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是集中精神的一种手段罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这么热的天 亏他们还能这么好动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有纪律 他们的教官在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推测 儿童的训练没有教官参与
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要如何将他们培养成社会的一员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请下达下一个命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好诈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到天上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务执行出现障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请批准排除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意不要对他们造成伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 状态怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命 中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待命中？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:07:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么？你在做什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道还做啊 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思议的材料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希迪亚斯 指甲 这颗星球 上 没有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的 话 就 送给 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我们边走边聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有好礼物可以送给弟弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟 弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的手很巧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何谓「弟弟」？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「弟弟」…就是兄弟的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比自己小的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家 人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旧社会中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基于雌雄配偶及血缘关系而构成的社会单位的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有过这样的习俗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德没有家人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低 效率 不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低效率…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得雷德住的地方很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔好像想问你关于宇宙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙 的 事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他对天体啦 还有能飞向宇宙的交通工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他身体很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无法自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身 体 虚弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的胸部有点疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在银河同盟中 体弱的人类将会被淘汰及处分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法参加战斗的人是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用…怎么能这样 雷德你无所谓吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不 懂 你 的提 问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是否能从与那个人的对话中得到有意义的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 就去见见奥尔德姆医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔 德姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个医生 不过大家都称他为贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是加尔刚蒂亚里知识最渊博的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 奥尔德姆医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生 艾米来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我带了客人来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道就是雷德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说有事想问问医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我还有工作没有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德 一会儿我会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下面等着我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方希望你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是听到过传言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是能理解语言的机械所发出的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这项技术已经失传了 没想到能亲眼看到实物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 可以 提问 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我能回答得上 你就尽管问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请教如何才能回到银河同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:11:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 以我的知识无法回答你的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见 大部分古老的智慧都已失传
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是行星穿梭技术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们目前所保留的关于天空的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.81,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它应该不是你所要找寻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 帮不上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 也没 办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 可以再 问 一个 问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 请说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.32,0:11:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想听听你对这个舰团组织的见解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓见解是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰团非常没有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令体系以及军事训练也不完善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民的行动也毫无秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法理解保护弱者的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星来客是这样看的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所指的效率似乎相当狭义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不妨去见见贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是否能从与那个人的对话中得到有意义的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否有意义应该由你自己判断
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PartB
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 医生也不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,630)}欢迎回来 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人就是雷德哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的是姐姐的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次 见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是艾米的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德也说想见见贝贝尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我方希望你提供情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚那个 难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这就是Chamber的通信机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 真的会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Chamber先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本机是用于支援驾驶员的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好酷 地球的语言也能理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人手不够了 你快来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 帅哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我得去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得现在气氛正好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么气氛正好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说不是你想的那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 贝贝尔 雷德就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太急了 小心摔倒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 姐姐总是匆匆忙忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德哥哥 你真的是从宇宙来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的生活是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河同盟的主要任务是与希迪亚斯进行战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希迪亚斯是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁人类生存的异种生物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们一直在战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从银河同盟创立至今 战斗从未停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这里的生活完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不堪消耗者唯有死亡一途
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 真的很艰辛呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你习惯这里的生活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法理解加尔刚蒂亚的组织构造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请解释低效及无意义经营的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰团不是组织啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是大家聚在一起罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时而吵架 时而互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以这样的方式活下去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问意义何在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都能安心地活着不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此回答感到不解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的行动目的应该是讨伐敌人希迪亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则人类无法获得稳定的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在银河同盟中 你这样的人类会立刻被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淘汰…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果将希迪亚斯全部都消灭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河同盟会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德哥哥你会怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在收到下一道命令之前待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 如果没有下一道命令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有继续待命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就和我们一样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.28,0:16:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为待命不就是指一直活下去的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你的人形机器人被乔给抢走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得当了次英雄 现在却不成样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道自己的行动是否有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是帮我们赶走海贼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我只是在监视Chamber而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是还没适应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法判断我应该采取什么行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该采取的行动啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先放弃你那军人思维怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放 弃？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 更加自由地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收集雨水！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是气象现象 没有毒性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生紧急事态了 用你的人形机器人来收集雨水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡水可是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有帆布 把它展开来收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 就这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵官的脑波产生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在意友军的战况
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在目前状况下 贵官的思考毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他果然好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 总觉得他好可怜…一个人流落到陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个帅哥没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:18:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你很担心他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你湿透了呢 会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我家把身体擦干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的骤雨很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次观测到集中降雨现象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙中也会下雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这样的病人也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我并不认为自己是不被需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢 还有姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾 米？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德哥哥也是一直被别人所需要才能活到现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有对战斗有益的人才需要存活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 反向思考一下 对雷德哥哥来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有你觉得需要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和姐姐 彼此都需要对方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是 我需要我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对同盟而言 无意义者没有生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这对你来说是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听姐姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道这是什么 却在制作着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是笛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗中完全不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笛 子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 它可以发出声音哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷德哥哥？你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说错什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是 我也不 知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是想起什么悲伤的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 这样 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.70,0:21:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你 把它 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是纱雅推荐的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chamber 还是无法定位坐标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观测情报不足 仍需要时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还需要进一步了解这个星球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要 贵官早晚将与主力部队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道的
